    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"for-the-pack\">For the Pack</h3><p>The Tenrō Clan are wielders of a unique bloodline ability which allows them to transform into a hybrid animal, most often a wolf or another land predator. As one of the founding clans of Yumegakure, the village hidden among dreams, the Tenrō clan stand as loyal allies to their homeland, a sacred land which they guard fiercely.</p><h4 id=\"tenr-traits\">Tenrō Traits</h4><hr /><ul><li><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Str or Dex, +1 Con</li><li><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 35.</li><li><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Martial Arts, Survival</li></ul>",
